vulnerabilities.title: js-ini Prorotype Pollution when malicious INI files submitted to an application that parses it with `parse`
vulnerabilities.description: This affects the package js-ini before 1.3.0. If an attacker submits a malicious INI file to an application that parses it with `parse` , they will pollute the prototype on the application. This can be exploited further depending on the context.
